<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink103-kilavi">
        aṟattoṭu niṉṟapiṉpu varaivāṉpirinta talaimakaṉ kaṭitiṉ vāratavaḻi aiyuṟṟacevili avaṉ nummaittuṟantāṉpōlum; nuṅkaṭku avaṉ kūṟiyatiṟam yātu eṉṟāṭkut tōḻi colliyatu. </p>      <p xml:lang="en">
          Spoken by the confident to her - the foster mother [was was] full of doubt when the hero who separated because of the marriage did not come [back] quickly [even] after standing with the truth, ‘ who said, ‘it seems he has abandoned us. What is the reason he said to you?’</p> </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink109">
<l>aṉṉai vāḻivēṇ ṭaṉṉai neyta</l>
<l>ṉīrppaṭar tūmpiṉ pūkkeḻu tuṟaiva</l>
<l>ṉentō ṭuṟanta kālai yevaṉkol</l>
<l>paṉṉāḷ varumava ṉaḷitta poḻutē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>  Oh mother, please mother,</l>
<l>When the man of the ghat with flowers</l>
<l>Of Neytal with stamen that spread over the water</l>
<l>Abandoned my shoulders,</l>
<l>What will come for many days? -- </l>
<l>[Thoughts of] those times when he was generous?!</l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
